Numix WHite cis a modern looking flat theme for Gnome. It supports Gnome, Unity, Pantheon, XFCE and Openbox. The theme is compatible with GTK 3.6. It also includes a GTK 2.0 theme using Murrine engine.

It is based of the original Numix theme, but has a whiter, cleaner look.

---

Installation Instructions:

Extract the zip file to the themes directory i.e. "/usr/share/themes/"
Alternatively, extract it to the ".themes" directory in your home folder if you want the theme to be applied only to you user.

Use a theme changer such as Gnome Tweak Tool, Ubuntu Tweak or LXappearance to change the the theme to Numix White

